  <!-- 30 Second Summary Takeaway -->
  <h2 id="summary-takeaway">30 Second Summary Takeaway</h2>

  <p>Alfa Laval centrifuges from Dolphin include manual-clean disc stack centrifuges, self-cleaning disc stack centrifuges, stainless steel centrifuges, decanter centrifuges, and auxiliary systems. Manual-clean models suit low-solids liquid-liquid service, while self-cleaning models automatically discharge separated sludge for higher-throughput operation. Stainless steel models serve chemical, sanitary, food-grade, and biotech applications, and decanters handle high-solids sludge, slurry, wastewater, and process streams.</p>

  <!-- Solid Bowl / Manual Clean -->
  <h2 id="solid-bowl">Alfa Laval Solid Bowl aka Manual Clean Centrifuges</h2>

  <p>Manual clean disc stack centrifuges use a solids-retaining bowl that holds separated sludge until the unit is stopped for cleaning. Their simpler bowl design eliminates the hydraulic sludge ejection system, which makes them easier to install, maintain, and operate. These machines are well suited for continuous liquid-liquid separation where solids are low or negligible. They are a practical choice for straightforward applications that value simplicity and serviceability.</p>

