  <h2 id="self-cleaning">Alfa Laval Auto-Desludging aka Self-Cleaning Centrifuges</h2>

  <p>Self-cleaning disc stack centrifuges are built for continuous separation of liquids and suspended solids in demanding industrial service. The bowl opens intermittently to discharge separated sludge automatically, allowing long operating cycles without frequent manual intervention. A hydraulic operating system controls the opening and closing sequence at predetermined intervals. This design is ideal for higher-throughput applications that need efficient, automated solids removal.</p>

