  <!-- Decanter / Horizontal Bowl -->
  <h2 id="decanter">Alfa Laval Decanter aka Horizontal Bowl Centrifuges</h2>

  <p>Decanter centrifuges are continuous industrial separators designed to remove solids from liquids using high centrifugal force inside a rotating horizontal bowl. A screw conveyor rotates at a differential speed to move settled solids toward the discharge end while clarified liquid exits separately. This design makes decanters especially effective for high-solids applications such as sludge thickening, dewatering, waste streams, and process slurries. They are a strong fit where continuous operation, rugged solids handling, and dependable throughput are the priority.</p>

